Package: scleaner
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: simple GNU/Linux desktop cleaner
 scleaner is a small utility which aim is to help the user to clean a GNU/Linux
 desktop. It is able to remove, for example, unwanted logs, orphan or duplicate
 files.
 .
 scleaner is based on a plugin system, which lets you search for files to be
 removed and act on these files.
 .
 scleaner can be used both as a normal-user and as root.
